org.gbif.occurrence.parsing.dwca

Class BufferedDwcaParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.occurrence.parsing.dwca.BufferedDwcaParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<RawOccurrenceRecord>, Iterator<RawOccurrenceRecord>

    public class BufferedDwcaParser
extends Object
implements Iterator<RawOccurrenceRecord>, Iterable<RawOccurrenceRecord>
    Reads a Darwin Core Archive using the dwca-reader package, and parses it into RawOccurrenceRecords. Reads the file using a size-configurable, asynchronously filled buffer to reduce memory requirements when reading enormous archives. Emphatically not thread-safe.
